    Return dictionary containing
        "success" as true
        "connection" as "quic_connection_handle"
        "stream_id" as "stream_001"

Process called "create_ipc_channel" that takes local as String and remote as String returns Dictionary:
    Note: Platform-specific IPC channel creation
    Return dictionary containing
        "success" as true
        "channel" as "ipc_channel_handle"
        "pipe_id" as "pipe_001"

Process called "json_stringify" that takes data as Any returns String:
    Note: Platform-specific JSON serialization
    Return "json_serialized_channel_data"

Process called "string_representation" that takes data as Any returns String:
    Note: Platform-specific string representation
    Return "string_repr"

