Process called "aes_256_encrypt" that takes data as String and key as String returns String:
    Note: Platform-specific AES-256 encryption
    Return data plus "_encrypted"

Process called "get_current_channel_bandwidth_usage" that takes channel_id as String returns Integer:
    Note: Platform-specific bandwidth usage tracking
    Return 512

Process called "send_tcp_data" that takes channel as Channel and data as String returns Dictionary:
    Note: Platform-specific TCP data transmission
    Return dictionary containing
        "success" as true
        "bytes_sent" as length of data

Process called "send_websocket_data" that takes channel as Channel and data as String returns Dictionary:
